            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_61gc' title='Col. 61GC &mdash; HL Deb 13 January 2004 vol 657 c61GC' name='column_61gc' href='#column_61gc' rel='bookmark'>61GC</a>
            consider very serious. I shall read the debate in <span class="italic">Hansard.</span> For the moment, however, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
